fields/help_text_en:
Acronym of Aggregation is composed of:
  • 2-4 letters + 2A
Examples: ARKE2A, BIOL2A, HIST2A
fields/help_text_fr:
Sigle d’une Aggégation est composé de:
  • 2-4 lettres + 2A
Examples: ARKE2A, BIOL2A, HIST2A

Examples: ACHA8FC, BARO8FC, CHAN8FC
